<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>Your Order Has Been Delivered!</title>
   <style>
      body {
         font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
         background-color: #0b0f19;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 0;
         color: #e2e8f0;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
         max-width: 600px;
         margin: 30px auto;
         background-color: #111827;
         border-radius: 16px;
         overflow: hidden;
         box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
         border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      }
      .header {
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
         padding: 40px 30px;
         text-align: center;
         color: #ffffff;
      }
      .logo {
         max-height: 48px;
         margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .header h2 {
         margin: 0;
         font-size: 26px;
         font-weight: 700;
         letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      .content {
         padding: 40px 30px;
         line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .content h1 {
         color: #10b981;
         font-size: 22px;
         margin-top: 0;
         font-weight: 600;
      }
      .highlight-box {
         background-color: #1f2937;
         border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
         padding: 20px;
         border-radius: 8px;
         margin: 25px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box table {
         width: 100%;
         border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      .highlight-box td {
         padding: 6px 0;
         font-size: 15px;
      }
      .highlight-box td.label {
         color: #9ca3af;
         font-weight: 500;
      }
      .highlight-box td.value {
         color: #f3f4f6;
         font-weight: 600;
         text-align: right;
      }
      .cta-button {
         display: block;
         background-color: #10b981;
         color: #ffffff !important;
         text-decoration: none;
         padding: 14px 30px;
         font-size: 16px;
         font-weight: 600;
         border-radius: 8px;
         margin: 30px auto;
         text-align: center;
         box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
         max-width: 200px;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .footer {
         background-color: #0d131f;
         padding: 25px 30px;
         text-align: center;
         font-size: 13px;
         color: #6b7280;
         border-top: 1px solid #1f2937;
      }
      .footer a {
         color: #10b981;
         text-decoration: none;
         font-weight: 500;
      }
   </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
         <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dbgrq28js/image/upload/v1736763971/logoipsum-282_ilqjfb_paw4if.png" alt="NextMart Logo" />
         <h2>Package Delivered!</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
         <h1>Hi {{userName}},</h1>
         <p>Great news! Your package has been successfully delivered. We hope you love your new purchase!</p>
         
         <div class="highlight-box">
            <table>
               <tr>
                  <td class="label">Order ID</td>
                  <td class="value">#{{orderId}}</td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td class="label">Total Amount Paid</td>
                  <td class="value">${{totalAmount}}</td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td class="label">Delivery Status</td>
                  <td class="value" style="color: #10b981;">Delivered / Completed</td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>

         <p>Your opinion matters greatly to our community. Could you take a moment to share your experience? Rate and review your purchased products to help other buyers make informed choices!</p>
         
         <a href="https://next-mart-client-sable.vercel.app/dashboard/my-orders" class="cta-button">Write a Review</a>

         <p>If you have any issues with your delivery or the products received, please contact our support team immediately by replying to this email.</p>
         <p>Thank you for choosing NextMart!</p>
         <p>Warm regards,<br><strong>The NextMart Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
         <p>© 2026 NextMart Ltd. Level-4, 34, Awal Centre, Banani, Dhaka.</p>
         <p>This is an automated delivery notification. Please do not reply directly to this message unless you need customer support.</p>
      </div>
   </div>
</body>
</html>
